omy</a></div></div></td></li></ul>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 0.1em 0.4em\">\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\" style=\"border:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;text-align: center\">Related articles</div><div class=\"NavContent\" style=\"font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center\">\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/wiki/Original_affluent_society\" title=\"Original affluent society\">Original affluent society</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/The_formalist_vs_substantivist_debate\" title=\"The formalist vs substantivist debate\">Formalist vs substantivist debate</a></li>\n<li> <i><a href=\"/wiki/The_Great_Transformation_(book)\" title=\"The Great Transformation (book)\">The Great Transformation</a></i></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Peasant_economics\" title=\"Peasant economics\">Peasant economics</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Culture_of_poverty\" title=\"Culture of poverty\">Culture of poverty</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Political_economy_in_anthropology\" title=\"Political economy in anthropology\">Political economy</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/State_formation\" title=\"State formation\">State formation</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Nutritional_anthropology\" title=\"Nutritional anthropology\">Nutritional anthropology</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Heritage_commodification\" title=\"Heritage commodification\">Heritage commodification</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/wiki/Anthropology_of_development\" title=\"Anthropology of development\">Anthropology of development</a></div></div></td></li></ul>\n</tr><tr><td style=\"padding:0 0.1em 0.4em\">\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\" style=\"border:none;padding:0\"><div class=\"NavHead\" style=\"font-size:105%;background:transparent;text-align:left;text-align: center\">Major theorists</div><div class=\"NavContent\" style=\"font-size:105%;padding:0.2em 0 0.4em;text-align:center\">\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/wiki/Paul_Bohannan\" title=\"Paul Bohannan\">Paul Bohannan